step_data.action: stop('After comparing all available map styles (Standard, CyclOSM, ÖPNVKarte, and Humanitarian) at various zoom levels, I found that the CyclOSM style provides the most detail for urban areas. It shows more building details, street-level information, and points of interest compared to the other styles. The Humanitarian style is also good for urban details but focuses more on essential infrastructure. The Standard style offers a balanced view, while ÖPNVKarte emphasizes public transportation routes but has less detail for other urban features.')
